# ─── node_modules ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never send host node_modules to the Docker daemon. The Dockerfile runs
# pnpm install inside the container. Host node_modules may have binaries
# compiled for the wrong OS/CPU architecture.
**/node_modules

# ─── Build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated inside the container during the build stage. Copying from host
# would overwrite the container's own build output.
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/out

# ─── Environment / secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NEVER bake .env files into an image — they contain secrets.
# Pass env vars at runtime via docker run --env-file, ECS task definitions,
# Kubernetes secrets, etc.
**/.env
**/.env.*
# Allow the example templates (they contain no real secrets)
!**/.env.example

# ─── Version control ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore

# ─── Test files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/__tests__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
**/test
**/coverage

# ─── Editor / OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.vscode
.idea
*.swp

.env.production
# ─── Docs / misc ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
README.md
docs/
*.log

# # ─── npm config ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# # .npmrc may contain auth tokens or private registry URLs. Never bake these into
# .npmrc
# **/.npmrc